{"tid":2239083,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"李嘉誠與施永青的分別 - 馮睎乾","createTime":"2020-10-11T15:37:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T07:34:42.000Z","uid":25558,"like":42,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9536d346b05f6c63c07cb29f50f0cd684e4c2e19","tid":2239083,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T15:37:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201011/5CXISTGPMVB3ZLDFZ6RPBSNJFM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201011%2F5CXISTGPMVB3ZLDFZ6RPBSNJFM%2F&d=aqHBcmSoErOqRK7CI6xlBZS3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=fc3f2496\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201011%2F5CXISTGPMVB3ZLDFZ6RPBSNJFM%2F&h=ec9d9f04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201011/5CXISTGPMVB3ZLDFZ6RPBSNJFM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n李嘉誠與施永青的分別 - 馮睎乾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/SK7dtnRtsqOKqU7lnUGMWO19Ioc=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QJH7SG32LJBX3ACFCZTK5SPNM4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FSK7dtnRtsqOKqU7lnUGMWO19Ioc%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQJH7SG32LJBX3ACFCZTK5SPNM4.jpg&h=ff1201f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n十月七日，加州柏克萊大學的Jennifer Doudna教授榮獲諾貝爾化學獎，阿爾伯特大學的Michael Houghton教授榮獲諾貝爾醫學獎，李嘉誠得知消息後，高興得流下眼淚。原來早於2010年和2011年，李嘉誠已慧眼識英雄，資助兩位教授的研究工作，等待十年，終於開花結果，難怪心情激動。李嘉誠基金會在網上發文說，李先生「相信二人的科研方向」，「感謝他們及團隊的努力，為世界帶來改變和希望。」<br />\n<br />\n沒有比較，就沒有傷害。同一天，也是靠地產發跡的施永青，則洋洋自得地在自己辦的報紙上，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n我也不妨簡單地把有錢人分為兩類，一類是成功的富人，一類是失敗的土豪。前者像李嘉誠，懂得善用財富，自強不息，日新其德，促進世界文明；後者像施永青，只計個人利益，抱殘守缺，自以為是，成為社會負累。有什麼比貧窮更可悲呢？就是窮得只有錢。有什麼比無知更愚蠢呢？就是賣弄錯誤的知識。<br />\n<br />\n成功的富人都尊重知識，虛懷若谷，喜歡聆聽「與自己生活經驗不一致的概念」，。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n當然，我批評施永青，不代表我認為年輕人一定對。事實上任何人也可能犯錯，無分尊卑貴賤，施永青的愚昧，在於他用年齡決定智愚，以舊日的經驗否定未來的變革。世界在變，人類對世界的認知也在變，地球決不是繞着藍絲廢老的「生活經驗」轉動的。文明的進步，總源於對固有經驗的懷疑和挑戰。一個民族若缺乏自由的思想、獨立的精神、批判的勇氣，那就永遠不可能進步，而一味標榜昔日經驗、維護既得利益的「成功人士」，說穿了就是這個民族的害群之馬。<br />\n<br />\n試看諾貝爾科學獎歷年得主，哪一個不是提出「與經驗不一致的概念」的？。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。炸，之前已有宇宙，天地乾坤本是無始無終的存在。彭羅斯認同這是crazy idea，但他也說： &ldquo;But maybe a crazy idea is what we need!&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n真正成功的人都不抗拒crazy idea，而不知道自己失敗的人，總以為經驗就是真理。施永青們不知道自己風生水起，不是因為你荷蘭叻，只因為投胎夠早，恰巧趕上七運的順風車。如今時移世易，標誌着「文明」和「疾變」的九運將臨，於是在七運雞犬升天的社會賢達、成功人士，都一個接一個在今天這「過渡期」露出本來面目。不出數年，這群人必然逃不過時代巨輪的輾壓，以及文明烈火的滌蕩。大江東去，浪淘盡下流人物，對於未來，李嘉誠和施永青都下注了，你寧願相信誰？"},{"pid":"857c84ff542fd3f311e25b5973203b5c4e3f5ae9","tid":2239083,"uid":311837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T15:47:59.000Z","msg":"誠哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34ddb483ebd58acdf13fafadb7055ffab1403874","tid":2239083,"uid":253016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T15:53:42.000Z","msg":"賤畜廢老一定要收皮"},{"pid":"12481987d93d513d4a0869829c0deeb2945c8937","tid":2239083,"uid":34949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T15:57:46.000Z","msg":"聖誕快樂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ba53ce69bf1709e17fbec014963c08c6ba289f4","tid":2239083,"uid":43751,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T15:59:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"17c8fe20727060ecb7e066fa16bd31a67b05fca6","tid":2239083,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T16:01:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇佢捐錢比十一哥run佢個死人黨 都知佢咩眼光喇"},{"pid":"5a7f1ba22afac386462f1d030ad5d801151ffe73","tid":2239083,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T16:11:25.000Z","msg":"但年輕時施永青係馬克思信徒,參與67,充滿理想<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"489e3506ad1ca72e874ad3ef082d0fbfa18a19cd","tid":2239083,"uid":196222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0ba53ce69bf1709e17fbec014963c08c6ba289f4","tid":2239083,"uid":43751,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T15:59:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T05:38:40.000Z","msg":"一個 3年前就已經成棟中環中心放售<br />\n一個只係K型樓市既寄生蟲大代理之一<br />\n<br />\n分別差好遠"},{"pid":"b4c0fcf85f1c6651164997c9f8958d6738de6fd0","tid":2239083,"uid":66202,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T05:49:32.000Z","msg":"痴線兩個lv差咁遠比較嚟有咩意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7114a1e5cfd2a9059db85f06a8187e203ec1c1e5","tid":2239083,"uid":127478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T07:13:04.000Z","msg":"無得比"},{"pid":"64f87c09889731914f34c66c4284b17cad41a35b","tid":2239083,"uid":14065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T07:14:20.000Z","msg":"咁樣叫節錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bfb79eca6710ac061acac50368cf3ea1471a2bd","tid":2239083,"uid":129340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4c0fcf85f1c6651164997c9f8958d6738de6fd0","tid":2239083,"uid":66202,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T05:49:32.000Z","msg":"痴線兩個lv差咁遠比較嚟有咩意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T07:15:36.000Z","msg":"悔肉左誠哥"},{"pid":"797feed68301e07f9a35b62f125be6c4e58df7e8","tid":2239083,"uid":185651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T07:15:51.000Z","msg":"聖誕快樂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"